# Multi-Agent RL for Distributed Scheduling

## Overview

**Level:** Advanced  
**Duration:** 150 minutes  
**Prerequisites:** deep_rl_algorithms, Distributed systems

Design and implement multi-agent systems for distributed scheduling

## Learning Objectives

By completing this module, you will be able to:
- Hands On Implementation
- Research Methods

## Prerequisites Check

Before starting this module, ensure you have:
- [ ] deep_rl_algorithms
- [ ] Distributed systems

